            <img class="img-right case-img" src="~/Content/images/CaseStudies/Overland Trail.png" />
            <strong>Overland Trail</strong>
            <br />
            <br />
            <strong>Background and Objectives</strong>
            <p>This 48 unit low income multifamily housing complex faced wasteful energy utilities and unhealthy living conditions.   The green upgrades used energy savings to subsidize urgently needed maintenance work on this building. The crawlspace was uninsulated and with significant moisture issues that ultimately would have led to serious damage. This project highlights ResourceSmart's approach, combining environmental upgrades with economic prosperity and social benefits.</p>
            <a href="~/Content/docs/Overland Trail Case Study.pdf" target="_blank">Click here to read the full study</a>
