            <strong>Reserve at Water Tower Village</strong>
            <br />
            <br />
            <strong>Background and Objectives</strong>
            <p>This multifamily housing unit located in Arvada CO suffered from high utility costs due to inefficient measures on the property. ResourceSmart was able to secure outside funding from multiple sources which made the retrofit more affordable for the owners upfront. This combined with the energy savings provided by the project made the property more affordable for the owners and the residents.</p>
            <a href="~/Content/docs/Reserve at Water Tower Village RS Arvada new.pdf" target="_blank">Click here to read the full study</a>
