            <strong>Arvada Place</strong>
            <br />
            <br />
            <strong>Background and Objectives</strong>
            <p>In 2014 a full green retrofit was completed on this 42 unit multi-family housing complex. A substantial portion of the costs were secured by ICAST through outside grants which allowed the energy efficiency upgrades to be affordable, and to save the affordable housing residents money in the long term.</p>
            <a href="~/Content/docs/Arvada Place Case Study RSARVADA.pdf" target="_blank">Click here to read the full study</a>
