            <strong>Greenleaf Apartments</strong>
            <br />
            <br />
            <strong>Background and Objectives</strong>
            <p>Greenleaf Apartments, a 55 unit multistory apartment complex in Aurora CO, provided a powerful example of how green rehab can do more than just improve the efficiency.  In their meetings with ICAST’s energy efficiency training team, residents have consistently reported enjoying higher quality of life at Greenleaf after the completion of the project. The low-income residents of the facility have thus benefitted in a manner that will help to perpetuate better life outcomes for residents through enhanced safety and a greater sense of community.</p>
