            <img class="img-right case-img" src="~/Content/images/CaseStudies/Viking Square.jpg"/>
            <strong>Viking Square</strong>
            <br />
            <br />
            <strong>Background and Objectives</strong>
            <p>Viking Square, a 55 unit, 3 building apartment complex in Arvada CO, showed clearly a high energy savings from the bringing in of new technology. This multifamily apartment complex was built in 1972 and the buildings heating system and cooling system were all still the original units when ResourceSmart made its initial assessment of the property. The combination of replacing the outdated equipment with energy efficient technology proved to drastically reduce the energy costs of the complex.</p>
